      "dimensions": 1,
      "description": "smooth - If the Pitch Control channel input to the Audio Oscillator  is rising and is running at the Touch default of 60 frames per second, then the pitch will hold for 1/60 second before stepping up for another 1/60 second. This is an audible step. With this option On, the pitch rises for every audio sample, giving perfectly smooth glissando at extra compute cost.",
      "tooltip": "",
      "help": "",
